  • Reference

    Municipality info (legacy)

    cadmun.Rd

    A dataset containing the municipality codes. The database is outdated, as it does not consider all municipalities.

    cadmun

    Format

    a data frame with 5657 rows e 35 variables:

    information about border, Amazon, capital, longitude, latitude, among others

    Source

    cadmun
